t;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;â”‚  â”œâ”€ [zone]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;â”œâ”€ third_party&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;v8srcapi&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;v8/src/api&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;v8/src/api&lt;/code&gt; directory in the V8 codebase is part of the V8 API. The V8 API provides functions for compiling and executing scripts, accessing C++ methods and data structures, handling errors, and enabling security checksÂ¹.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
